## Scripts (pnpm)

- Build/serve: `pnpm build`, `pnpm dev`, `pnpm preview`
- Deploy: `pnpm deploy` (wrangler deploy)
- Tests: `pnpm test`, `pnpm test:watch`, `pnpm test:ui`
- Lint/format: `pnpm lint`, `pnpm format`, `pnpm typecheck`
- Docs: `pnpm docs:dev`, `pnpm docs:build`, `pnpm docs:preview`

## Cloudflare setup snippets

- Create R2 bucket: `pnpm wrangler r2 bucket create turborepo-cache`
- Set secret: `echo "SECRET" | pnpm wrangler secret put TURBO_TOKEN`

See [package.json](mdc:package.json) and [README.md](mdc:README.md) for details.
